effect.title: Node Pool Spec Template Spec Startup Taints Effect
effect.description: Required. The effect of the taint on pods that do not tolerate the taint. Valid effects are NoSchedule, PreferNoSchedule and NoExecute.

key.description: Required. The taint key to be applied to a node.

time_added.description: TimeAdded represents the time at which the taint was added.

value.description: The taint value corresponding to the taint key.

NodePoolSpecTemplateSpecStartupTaints.title: Node Pool Spec Template Spec Startup Taints
NodePoolSpecTemplateSpecStartupTaints.description: The node this Taint is attached to has the "effect" on any pod that does not tolerate the Taint.
